<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .logo {
            max-width: 150px;
        }
        .payment-button {
            display: block;
            width: 200px;
            background-color: #1b3f6d;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 12px 20px;
            margin: 25px auto;
            border-radius: 5px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .pharmacy-box {
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #777;
            text-align: center;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <img src="https://d2x163e8fostr4.cloudfront.net/common/WebLogo.svg" alt="Company Logo" class="logo">
    </div>

    <p>Dear <%= patient_name %>,</p>

    <p>You have received a payment request from the pharmacy below to dispense your prescribed medication:</p>
    
    <div class="pharmacy-box">
        <p><strong>Pharmacy Name:</strong> <%= pharmacy_name %></p>
        <p><strong>Address:</strong> <%= pharmacy_address_line_1 %>, <%= pharmacy_address_line_2 %>, <%= pharmacy_city %>, <%= pharmacy_state %></p>
        <p><strong>Contact:</strong> <%= pharmacy_contact %></p>
        <p><strong>Email:</strong> <%= pharmacy_email %></p>
    </div>

    <p>To proceed, please click the button below to complete the payment:</p>

    <a href="<%= link %>" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="payment-button">Pay Now</a>

    <p>If you did not request this or believe this message was sent in error, please ignore this email.</p>

    <div class="footer">
        <p>Warm regards,<br>The Sendscript Team</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
